title: 211: Monday Night Football Recap, Saquon Barkley Breakdown
itunes:title: 211: Monday Night Football Recap, Saquon Barkley Breakdown
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks recap the Dallas Cowboys' 28-17 win over the Arizona Cardinals on Monday night (:50). The guys also break down Penn State running back Saquon Barkley (12:50), and share their takeaways from last weekend's college football games (17:00).
